cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.CR 

This paper discusses the use of wireless connectivity in the IoT scenario, specifically focusing on LPWANs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the efficiency and effectiveness of this approach, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The discussion of Smart Cities applications could also place the paper under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
